<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>PDF Fusion - Extended Employment Contract Template</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <%= stylesheet_link_tag 'application', media: 'all' %>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row template-container">
            <div class="card p-3">
                <h5 class="text-center">Standard Employment Contract</h5>
                <p>This contract outlines the general terms of employment between the employer and the employee.</p>
            

                <!-- Employer and Employee Details -->
                <p><strong>Employer:</strong> <i>[business_name]</i></p>
                <p><strong>Employee:</strong> <i>[employee_name]</i></p>
                <p><strong>Job Title:</strong> <i>[job_title]</i></p>
                <p><strong>Contract Duration:</strong> <i>[month]</i> months (commencing on <i>[start_date]</i> and ending on <i>[end_date]</i>)</p>
                <p><strong>Work Hours:</strong> 40 hours per week, Monday to Friday, from 9:00 AM to 5:00 PM, with a one-hour lunch break.</p>
                <p><strong>Salary:</strong> $20 per hour, payable bi-weekly on <i>[payment_date]</i> via direct deposit.</p>
            

                <!-- Job Responsibilities -->
                <h6 class="mt-3"><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></h6>
                <p>The employee agrees to carry out the following tasks with diligence and professionalism:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Perform duties as assigned by the employer or supervisor.</li>
                    <li>Adhere to company policies and procedures.</li>
                    <li>Maintain confidentiality of company information.</li>
                    <li>Attend all required meetings and training sessions.</li>
                    <li>Meet performance goals and deadlines.</li>
                </ul>
               

                <!-- Compensation and Benefits -->
                <h6 class="mt-3"><strong>Compensation and Benefits:</strong></h6>
                <p>In addition to the base salary, the employee is entitled to the following benefits:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Health insurance coverage after 90 days of employment.</li>
                    <li>Paid time off (PTO) of 10 days per year, accrued monthly.</li>
                    <li>401(k) retirement plan with employer matching up to 5% of the employee's salary.</li>
                    <li>Annual performance bonus, subject to company performance and employee evaluation.</li>
                </ul>
             

                <!-- Confidentiality Clause -->
                <h6 class="mt-3"><strong>Confidentiality:</strong></h6>
                <p>The employee agrees not to disclose any confidential information about the company, its clients, or its operations during or after the term of employment. This includes, but is not limited to, trade secrets, business strategies, and customer data.</p>
               

                <!-- Non-Compete Clause -->
                <h6 class="mt-3"><strong>Non-Compete Agreement:</strong></h6>
                <p>During the term of employment and for a period of 12 months after termination, the employee agrees not to engage in any business activities that directly compete with the employer.</p>
               

                <!-- Termination Clause -->
                <h6 class="mt-3"><strong>Termination:</strong></h6>
                <p>This contract may be terminated under the following conditions:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>By the employer, with 30 days' written notice or payment in lieu of notice.</li>
                    <li>By the employee, with 30 days' written notice.</li>
                    <li>Immediately, in cases of gross misconduct or breach of contract by either party.</li>
                </ul>
              

                <!-- Dispute Resolution -->
                <h6 class="mt-3"><strong>Dispute Resolution:</strong></h6>
                <p>Any disputes arising from this contract shall be resolved through mediation or arbitration in accordance with the laws of <i>[state/country]</i>.</p>
             

                <!-- Governing Law -->
                <h6 class="mt-3"><strong>Governing Law:</strong></h6>
                <p>This contract shall be governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of <i>[state/country]</i>.</p>
                

                <!-- Signatures -->
                <p class="text-muted">Both parties agree to the above terms.</p>
                <p>Signed by: __________________ (Employer) &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Date: <i>[signature_date]</i></p>
                <p>Signed by: __________________ (Employee) &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Date: <i>[employee_sign_date]</i></p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>